<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's no stranger to turning heads, both on-camera and at high-profile events.</p>

<p>And Kady McDermott looked typically stunning as she shared a photo from a recent spa trip to Instagram on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The Love Island star, 25, was the picture of confidence as she slipped into a tiny pink bikini while enjoying a hot tub session.</p>

<p>Watch her glow: Kady McDermott looked typically stunning as she shared a photo from a recent spa trip to Instagram on Tuesday</p>

<p>Showcasing her incredible figure, the media personality stunned in the two-piece, which featured a halterneck bralet and matching briefs.</p>

<p>The make-up artist ensured focus remained on her striking frame as she accessorised with dainty earrings.</p>

<p>With her tresses scraped into a ponytail, Kady displayed her naturally radiant complexion as she went make-up free.</p>

